ie.gmit.sw.Reflection

Class ListClass

  • java.lang.Object
    • ie.gmit.sw.Reflection.ListClass
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ListClassable

    public class ListClass
extends java.lang.Object
implements ListClassable
    A Customised List class that implements the ListClassable interface and delegates calls to the java.util.list package, which performs a number of required operations. Created and used to provide a good example of Composition and Delegation, ie that a metric to be calculated CalculateMetrics 'HAS-A' List of classes associated with it and that by implementing a customised version of the java.util.list class, demonstrates the use of Delegation.
